{"tid":1069300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【妓女都有口齒過你】美中下周展開新一輪貿易談判　傳美憂中國食言","createTime":"2019-03-20T01:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T02:16:06.000Z","uid":173631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a88653ed9882aac95e19fd3e5e9484dac7bc385","tid":1069300,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"中共世貿承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2018/3-29/p2130181a706831142-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2018%2F3-29%2Fp2130181a706831142-ss.jpg&h=3b65daa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190320/1536403/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190320%2F1536403%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9EbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=8d661b01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190320%2F1536403%2F&h=590866af\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190320/1536403/</a><br />\n席貿易談判代表萊特希澤（左）與中方代表劉鶴。路透<br />\n美國總統川普周二重申中美貿易談判進展良好之際，彭博新聞引述消息人士報導，有美國官員憂慮中國在貿易談判中改口。<br />\n <br />\n根據報導，中方貿易談判代表鑑於就算已經同意改革智慧財產權政策，但仍得不到川普政府保證撤銷對中國貨的關稅，於是改變立場。<br />\n <br />\n消息人士又指，中國在最初承諾的藥廠「數據保護制度」上退縮，又拒絕透露「專利連結制度（Patent Linkages）」詳情，而數據服務事宜亦拒絕讓步。北京又試圖加入確保協議規則遵守中國法律的字眼。<br />\n <br />\n報導指出，美國貿易代表署近日就中方保障智慧財產權承諾的措辭，向中方表示關注，要求中方處理。<br />\n <br />\n有美國官員視中國的舉動為出爾反爾，但亦有人認為那些只是談判過程的一部份。<br />\n <br />\n接近美國貿易代表萊特海澤（Robert Lighthizer）的人士，否認中國官員背棄承諾，而一名中國官員表示談判仍然進行中，討價還價份屬平常。<br />\n <br />\n另外，《華爾街日報》（WSJ）周二報導，美中計劃下周展開新一輪貿易談判，希望最晚在下月達成貿易協議。有美國政府官員表示，萊特海澤和財長馬鈕金（Steven Mnuchin）下周會到北京。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"b42f55135868fbc62c911aee1ee99476ffad400a","tid":1069300,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2415ee7ae268b21887dc12d8d1be88a6fcf75309","tid":1069300,"uid":77220,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xx5PE0h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxx5PE0h.gif&h=a4351c02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8e4a56b34241382bedbb0efc481ff46b59c111c","tid":1069300,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"傳下月達成協議<br />\n傳下月達成協議<br />\n傳下月達成協議<br />\n由上年年尾傳撚到而家都係傳下月達成協議<br />\n靠個傳字就推到個市升左五千點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01fcc68660739ee4492c8929a673489fcbc6942","tid":1069300,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42f55135868fbc62c911aee1ee99476ffad400a","tid":1069300,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"有咩比死更難受 就係生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵不愧為生意佬 真係好識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國有個咁嘅總統 真係國運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6930c8ee28fa29be880677d47d451a4e2fd35a8a","tid":1069300,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c01fcc68660739ee4492c8929a673489fcbc6942","tid":1069300,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42f55135868fbc62c911aee1ee99476ffad400a","tid":1069300,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"有咩比死更難受 就係生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵不愧為生意佬 真係好識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國有個咁嘅總統 真係國運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01: